stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> draft : 系统生成草稿

    draft --> submitted : 👤 用户确认提交
    draft --> [*] : 用户放弃

    submitted --> accepted : 🔧 服务站受理
    submitted --> cancelled : 👤 用户取消

    accepted --> assigned : 分配给服务顾问/技师
    accepted --> cancelled : 无效报修取消

    assigned --> contacting : 联系客户确认情况

    contacting --> waiting_vehicle : 等待车辆进站或救援到达

    waiting_vehicle --> inspecting : 🔧 车辆到站开始检测

    inspecting --> warranty_review : 需要判断质保归属
    inspecting --> quotation : 非质保项目出报价
    inspecting --> repairing : 明确故障直接维修

    warranty_review --> repairing : ✅ 质保通过，开始免费维修
    warranty_review --> quotation : 不在质保范围，转报价
    warranty_review --> factory_support : 疑难问题升级厂家

    factory_support --> repairing : 🏭 厂家给出方案，开始维修

    quotation --> repairing : 👤 客户确认报价
    quotation --> cancelled : 👤 客户拒绝报价

    repairing --> waiting_parts : 等待配件到货
    waiting_parts --> repairing : 配件到货继续维修

    repairing --> completed : 🔧 维修完成

    completed --> customer_confirmed : 👤 客户确认完成
    completed --> repairing : 客户验车发现问题，返修

    customer_confirmed --> closed : 🔚 工单正式关闭

    cancelled --> [*]
    closed --> [*]